OL,3,CWhy are we seeing this 40C heatwave
OL,4,Cand is it a sign of things to come?
OL,6,FForecasts suggest the UK will see the
OL,7,Fhottest June weather on record in the
OL,8,Fcoming days, with significant impacts
OL,9,Fon health and infrastructure.
OL,11,FBut why are we seeing such extreme
OL,12,Fheat, and will we see more of it in
OL,13,Fthe future?
OL,15,FWhat's making it so hot?
OL,17,FThe reason for our exceptionally high
OL,18,Ftemperatures is a knock-on effect from
OL,19,Fthe extreme heat currently being
OL,20,Fexperienced across a vast area of
OL,21,FEurope.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
