PN,31002
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782211684
OL,3,CWhy are we seeing this 40C heatwave
OL,4,Cand is it a sign of things to come?
OL,6,FThis is due to a 'heat dome', where
OL,7,Fhigh pressure over the continent is
OL,8,Fexacerbating the dangerously high
OL,9,Ftemperatures.
OL,11,FThis hot air originated in North
OL,12,FAfrica, and as it surges into Europe,
OL,13,Fit continues to heat up over the
OL,14,Fcontinental landmass.
OL,16,FAs the air compresses under the high
OL,17,Fpressure, it heats up even more,
OL,18,Fmaking temperatures in Europe 40-45C
OL,19,Fin many areas.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
