PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782211684
OL,3,CWhy are we seeing this 40C heatwave
OL,4,Cand is it a sign of things to come?
OL,6,FThis 'heat dome' is coming over to the
OL,7,FUK.
OL,9,FThe combination of this and high
OL,10,Fhumidity means the temperatures are
OL,11,Fextremely dangerous, with a rare red
OL,12,Fextreme heat warning being issued by
OL,13,Fthe Met Office for this week.
OL,15,FHow high will temperatures get?JThe
OL,16,Fforecast indicates highs of 36-38C for
OL,17,Fthree consecutive days, with a chance
OL,18,Fof it even reaching 40C.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
