PN,31004
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782211684
OL,3,CWhy are we seeing this 40C heatwave
OL,4,Cand is it a sign of things to come?
OL,6,FWhile the record for the hottest day
OL,7,Fis 40.3C in July 2022, there's a high
OL,8,Fchance the record-breaking June
OL,9,Ftemperatures recorded in 1976 will be
OL,10,Fbroken both by day and by night this
OL,11,Fweek.
OL,13,FDays will be uncomfortably hot and
OL,14,Fhumid in places, with very stuffy,
OL,15,Fmuggy and warm nights as temperatures
OL,16,Fare unlikely to drop much after the
OL,17,Fsevere daytime heating.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
