OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782211684
OL,3,CWhy are we seeing this 40C heatwave
OL,4,Cand is it a sign of things to come?
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FAfter the summer solstice yesterday,
OL,12,Fdays are at their longest, and the sun
OL,13,Fis at its strongest - both are factors
OL,14,Fwhich encourage these extraordinarily
OL,15,Fhigh temperatures.
OL,17,FThe heat and humidity will trigger
OL,18,Fthunderstorms in places, and the cloud
OL,19,Fgenerated by these could help cap
OL,20,Ftemperatures for some, but it will
OL,21,Fstay very warm, muggy and humid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
