CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782211684
OL,3,CWhy are we seeing this 40C heatwave
OL,4,Cand is it a sign of things to come?
OL,6,FAre these temperatures something we're
OL,7,Fgoing to see more of?
OL,9,FThe chance of temperatures exceeding
OL,10,F40C in the UK is accelerating, and it
OL,11,Fis now over 20 times more likely than
OL,12,Fit was in the 1960s, according to a
OL,13,Fnew Met Office study.
OL,15,FTemperatures used to regularly peak
OL,16,Faround 30-32C in July and August, as
OL,17,Fmany would remember headlines of 32C-
OL,18,F90F on the front pages of newspapers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
