FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31007
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782211684
OL,3,CWhy are we seeing this 40C heatwave
OL,4,Cand is it a sign of things to come?
OL,6,FNow we've seen a record high of 35C in
OL,7,Fthe spring during the May heatwave,
OL,8,Fand we will see higher temperatures
OL,9,Fagain this week.
OL,11,FThat's two consecutive months that the
OL,12,Fmonthly record temperature will be
OL,13,Fbroken by quite a margin.
OL,15,FTogether with high humidity, it'll
OL,16,Ffeel increasingly uncomfortable.
OL,18,FAs our climate continues to warm, we
OL,19,Fcan expect the chance of 40C heat to
OL,20,Fkeep rising.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
