PN,31008
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1782211684
OL,3,CWhy are we seeing this 40C heatwave
OL,4,Cand is it a sign of things to come?
OL,6,FProfessor Stephen Belcher CBE, Met
OL,7,FOffice Chief Scientist, said: "Human-
OL,8,Finduced climate change has made events
OL,9,Flike this more likely and more intense.
OL,11,F"To see temperatures like this in the
OL,12,FUK in June is sobering.
OL,14,F"Events like this bring home the
OL,15,Fimplications of climate change, with
OL,16,Fvery high temperatures and humidity
OL,17,Fbringing significant health
OL,18,Fimplications from heat stress, as well
OL,19,Fas impacts to a range of sectors such
OL,20,Fas transport, energy and water supply."
